caption:
No one tougher 😤

After undergoing knee surgery this summer, @kellyn_taylor returned to the New York City Marathon and finished 10th in 2:27:59. Kellyn has placed top ten in all five of her appearances in NYC. 🤯 Fellow @naz_elite teammate @aliphine dug deep and finished 19th in 2:32:10. 

On the men’s side, @marakwetexpress finished 16th in 2:11:58 with @bigfoot_sum close behind finishing 17th in 2:12:32. Congratulations, Team @NAZ_Elite! 🙌
